Keller Williams Bluegrass Realty - Lake Cumberland

data.description: Looking for a new home for the holidays?! Don't let this one pass you by! Whether you're a first time home buyer, looking to downsize, to invest, or even looking for a weekend getaway for vacations; this 2 bed 1 bath home is just waiting for you to make it your own. Conveniently located to all the amenities North Highway 27 has to offer; plus you can be at two of Pulaski Counties parks in 15 minutes or less to enjoy beautiful Lake Cumberland.  There is a shed on the property and the dog house out back, does convey. Property has a partially fenced in back yard, and the rest of the back yard has plenty of room just waiting for you to spend time in it on warm summer nights with friends and family!!  Call or text for a showing today!
